snippet: Dominic Thiem of Austria beat Rafael Nadal, 6-4, 4-6, 7-6 (4), on Saturday at the Argentina Open, a clay event in Buenos Aires.
abstract: Dominic Thiem defeats defending champion Rafael Nadal on clay court during Argentina Open; other tennis news and scores noted.
